(PH) {icon:bullet,1.2} When you take direct damage you instead only receive {c_number}[{SF_2}*100|%|]{/c} of it in the form of Poisoning over {c_number}{SF_3}{/c} seconds.

{icon:bullet,1.2} Enemies who move while Poisoned by you additionally take {c_number}[{SF_4}*100|%|]{/c} of your Thorns damage per second.
